

=Bio=

"I have a multiple background owing to the fact that my profile can be defined with three different adjectives: technical, planner, and social. My degree in Architecture, my professional experience in urban planning and my post graduate studies in urban geography help in building the structure of my triple profile which is the result of a wide-ranging academic, professional and personal engagements itinerary.

My passion, together with my persistence and commitment are the tools I use to make my dreams come true. And I do have a dream. I believe in a world where architects don't rise just building structures, but that we could be able to construct better habitats for people. And taking the risk to seem unrealistic I must believe in it. As Hesse said, "To achieve the possible, we must attempt the impossible again and again."


